{"tid":1394864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍天瑞邨一單位檢獲煙霧彈　單位內兩男一女被捕","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T15:59:00.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6de9d0af682ad94127a98b271f9b9190e758707f","tid":1394864,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:32:29.000Z","msg":"警方晚上在天水圍天瑞（二）邨瑞滿樓拘捕一男兩女涉嫌無牌藏有爆炸品，初步懷疑是一批煙霧彈，單位內兩男一女疑為家人關係，已被警方有組織罪案及三合會調查科拘捕，稍後會帶署調查及檢走有關證物。<br />\n<br />\n據報，警方爆炸品處理科在初步檢有關爆炸品後已離開。警方將於晚上11時向記者交代案情。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2417156/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2417156%2F&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=53b5bb5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2417156/</a>"},{"pid":"e0bb51110dfaaeb3528769693c3788e2423d5805","tid":1394864,"uid":269681,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:42:52.000Z","msg":"收埋係屋企都會有人知？"},{"pid":"b920b728e850cefa66a0ab5604a8c0e6f85f09df","tid":1394864,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e1ee2688f7c4756a7233c509f0cd5f5d8cf5b4","tid":1394864,"uid":131188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:48:58.000Z","msg":"煙霧滅蚤彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec33fba10694033c8f048ef320265e6b36ae020e","tid":1394864,"uid":152222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"我屋企有漂白水算唔算有大殺傷力化學武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d4d8b30d08d8de42b66a71833075454982ddc0","tid":1394864,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R1a0ce9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR1